Main states of game:

- Menu - some sort of place, where you can select something by selecting entries to change game settings, game state, or move to another main game state

- World - main, where you can prepare to journey. Travel the world, meet byches, eat them, and select which dungeon u want to visit next. Also, before each dungeon you can select, which Wordphrases you want to remember, to take with you. 
Remembrance - mechaanics, that allow to fortify you your wordspeaking abiblitous.

- Dungeon - map of dungeon, where players travels, gathers shit of putin and seeks for bychpower.

- Battle - place, where you can clean the face of enemy by destroying it.


